Deluxe CD/DVD digipak edition. 2013 release, the fourth album from the Thrash Metal band. Empires Collapse is the follow-up to their 2011 album Worlds Torn Asunder. The album was recorded with producer Steve Evetts (Sepultura, The Dillinger Escape Plan, Suicide Silence), mixed by Brett Eliason (Pearl Jam, Heart, Avenged Sevenfold) and mastered by Alan Douches/West West Side Music (Cannibal Corpse, Hatebreed, Converge). The album's cover artwork was designed by Adrienne Rozzi
